thread.title: D. George

author: D. George
title: D. George
text:
I was looking for a couple upgrades for Windows 10 Home to Pro, this was less expensive than the upgrades so I purchased a copy. After I installed a copy on a new pc, it appears to work well. I then purchased a second copy.
With that written, I did not give it 5 stars because it was a bit difficult to install, the instructions must be followed. You cannot load a copy directly from Microsoft using the provided key, you MUST use their copy of Windows 10 Pro.
